            <description><![CDATA[现在不少小伙伴家里都养猫猫狗狗，也常常出现被家里“逆子”抓、咬伤的情况<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[喵喵]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_miao-c1b3d563bd.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>一旦被宠物弄伤后，伤口该怎处理👇🏻 （<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>卫子提醒，被咬/抓伤后，绝不能用嘴去吸伤口哦<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃瓜]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chigua-7a95e6efc4.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#健康素养提升v计划#</span></a>（健康广东） <img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hiz9j1cv0oj20u03ya4q0.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hiz9j0jhv4j20wi0e8gmd.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
